strings: <voice_0x010015D1><se_high>Accuracy: A strange image appeared in my head. It's a desert... a giant skull... and dragons, isn't it? And glass beads...
<voice_0x010015D2><se_low>January: Perhaps a cave of dragons in the desert. Southern Aragon, correct? I'll go right away!
<voice_0x010015D3><se_high>Accuracy: Or not. Predator appears to be highly constitutive.
<voice_0x010015D4><se_low>King of tricks: It's not wise to listen to this clear message, it's nonsense. Let's prepare for a desert safari now!
<voice_0x010015D5><se_low>January: The Dragon Tomb is located on Laoxi Street. Let's do our best and get started!
